commit.message:
re PR tree-optimization/59617 ([vectorizer] ICE in vectorizable_mask_load_store with AVX-512F's gathers enabled.)

gcc/testsuite/

        PR target/59617
	* gcc.target/i386/avx512f-gather-2.c: Remove XPASS.
	* gcc.target/i386/avx512f-gather-5.c: Ditto.

From-SVN: r207274
